import { Card, CardHeader, CardBody, CardFooter, SimpleGrid, Text, Button, Heading, Grid } from '@chakra-ui/react'

function Result({ results }) {
    return (
        <Grid mt={15} templateColumns='repeat(3, 1fr)' gap={8}>
            {results &&
                results.map((result, index) => (
                    <Card key={index}>
                        <CardHeader>
                            <Heading size='md'>{result.title}</Heading>
                        </CardHeader>
                        <CardBody>
                            <Text>{result.description}</Text>
                        </CardBody>
                    </Card>
                ))}
            {/* <Card>

            </CardBody>
            </Card>
            
            <Card>

                    <Heading size='md'>Diagnosis Result</Heading>
                </CardHeader>
            <CardBody>
                <Text>View a summary of all your customers over the last month.</Text>
            </CardBody>
            </Card>
            
            <Card>
                <CardHeader>
                    <Heading size='md'>Diagnosis Result</Heading>
                </CardHeader>
            <CardBody>
                <Text>View a summary of all your customers over the last month.</Text>
            </CardBody>
            </Card> */}
            
        </Grid>
    );
}


export default Result;
